#. Add-on summary, usually the user visible name of the addon.
#. Translators: Summary for this add-on to be shown
#. on installation and add-on information.
#: buildVars.py:24
msgid "Contact Book for NVDA."
msgstr "Agenda de Contatos para NVDA."

#. Add-on description
#. Translators: Long description to be shown for this add-on
#. on add-on information from add-ons manager
#: buildVars.py:28
msgid ""
"This add-on creates an agenda where we can save phone numbers, e-mails of "
"people and companies that we deem necessary."
msgstr ""
"Este addon cria uma agenda onde podemos guardar números de telefone, e-mails "
"de pessoas e empresas que jugarmos necessário."

